    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she's a total beauty! This car is in truly flawless condition\u2014it still looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I've been incredibly meticulous with maintenance, always keeping it garaged and professionally detailed. There isn't a single scratch or blemish to be found. It runs like an absolute dream and is ready for its next adventure. I'd love for it to go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
