    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E46 M3, a definitive pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. This specimen features the S54 3.2L straight-six, utilizing six individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS to deliver a linear, high-revving powerband. The mechanical integrity is superlative: the rod bearings and subframe reinforcement have been proactively addressed, and the 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox provides precise, tactile engagement. The suspension geometry remains factory-spec with refreshed bushings and dampers, ensuring the legendary 50/50 weight distribution is fully realized. Finished in flawless Carbon Black, this vehicle displays zero clear coat failure or oxidation, with a pristine undercarriage and a cabin free of bolster wear or pixel degradation.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "2021 Model X. Single owner. Garage kept. No accidents. Pristine interior. Full service history. New tires. Ready to drive.",
