    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I'm selling my absolute pride and joy. This car is in truly incredible shape\u2014it honestly looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this beauty since day one, keeping it spotless and strictly following every single service schedule. It drives like a total dream and is ready for its next adventure. You seriously won't find another one this clean! Feel free to reach out if you want to take a look!",
      "price": 44500.0,
