    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, showcasing the pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. This specimen features the S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing six individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing for a razor-sharp throttle response and an 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers precise throw engagement, transmitting power to the rear wheels via a speed-sensitive variable M differential lock. The chassis is structurally immaculate, with a reinforced rear subframe and factory-spec bushings ensuring total torsional rigidity. Every kinematic component, from the MacPherson strut front suspension to the multi-link rear, remains in peak operating condition, delivering the communicative feedback and 50/50 weight distribution balance required by the most demanding purists.",
